[i]  [size=6] [color=#6aa84f]DOMAIN EXTENDED[/color][/size][/i][color=#6aa84f] [/color]                

[color=#6aa84f][size=4]DOMAIN EXTENDED[/size][/color] a Players home.

Entrance to [color=#6aa84f]DOMAIN[/color] see picture for info.

This is my last mod, i would like to thank all players that have down loaded my mods, and thank you to the players that endorsed them.To endorse any modders work gives the sign they are on the right track with there work,so please dont forget to endorse, modders give a lot of there free time to help advance and improve the game.


I have replaced the old [color=#6aa84f]DOMAIN[/color] mod with the new version [color=#6aa84f]DOMAIN EXTENDED[/color], there is a caven and a new world land you can now teleport to.
Delete the old [color=#6aa84f]DOMAIN[/color] then install [color=#6aa84f]DOMAIN EXTENDED[/color].

I have tested the navmesh with a follower and encountered no problems.

[color=#6aa84f][size=3]Fully navmeshed[/size][/color]

[color=#6aa84f][size=3]
Requirements:[/size][/color] Dawnguard.Hearthfire.Dragonborn.

[color=#6aa84f][size=3]
Installation:[/size][/color] Just download with Nexus mod manger, Mod organizer or manual,if you want to install it manually,
                       then you have to extract it into your data file for Skyrim.

[color=#6aa84f][size=3]
Unistallation:[/size][/color]  Just untick in mod manger or mod organzier or delete the files you manually installed.


[color=#6aa84f][size=5]
CREDITS:[/size] Many thanks to     "Malo Statues by Malo" 

                                               "cad435 for Snow Elves Remastered"

[color=#6aa84f]Cleaned[/color][/size][color=#6aa84f] with TES5Edit[/color].         

I hope you enjoy the home.

My Regards to you all.

Thank You.




I will if a can respond to any post if and when my busy life gives me the time to do so.
